                <article class="cc-card cc-result-card"><a class="cc-result-card__poster" href="/concerts/22"><img src="/images/sample/poster-triangle.svg" alt="세븐틴 포스터"></a><div class="cc-result-card__body"><span class="cc-concert-card__category">콘서트</span><h3 class="cc-result-card__title"><a href="/concerts/22">세븐틴 WORLD TOUR &lt;NEW_&gt; IN SEOUL</a></h3><p class="cc-result-card__line">2026.02.06(금) - 2026.02.08(일)</p><p class="cc-result-card__line">고척스카이돔</p><p class="cc-result-card__line">서울</p><p class="cc-rating"><span class="cc-rating__star">★</span> 4.8 (1,892)</p><span class="cc-badge">단독판매</span></div><button class="cc-heart" type="button">♡</button></article>
                <article class="cc-card cc-result-card"><a class="cc-result-card__poster" href="/concerts/1"><img src="/images/sample/poster-legend-seoul.svg" alt="무명전설 서울 포스터"></a><div class="cc-result-card__body"><span class="cc-concert-card__category">콘서트</span><h3 class="cc-result-card__title"><a href="/concerts/1">2026 무명전설 전국투어 콘서트 - 서울</a></h3><p class="cc-result-card__line">2026.06.27(토) - 2026.06.28(일)</p><p class="cc-result-card__line">올림픽공원 올림픽홀</p><p class="cc-result-card__line">서울</p><p class="cc-rating"><span class="cc-rating__star">★</span> 4.7 (956)</p><span class="cc-badge">단독판매</span></div><button class="cc-heart" type="button">♡</button></article>
                <article class="cc-card cc-result-card"><a class="cc-result-card__poster" href="/concerts/23"><img src="/images/sample/poster-artist.svg" alt="황치열 포스터"></a><div class="cc-result-card__body"><span class="cc-concert-card__category">콘서트</span><h3 class="cc-result-card__title"><a href="/concerts/23">황치열 전국투어 콘서트 &lt;별, 그대&gt; - 서울</a></h3><p class="cc-result-card__line">2026.03.14(토) - 2026.03.15(일)</p><p class="cc-result-card__line">세종대학교 대양홀</p><p class="cc-result-card__line">서울</p><p class="cc-rating"><span class="cc-rating__star">★</span> 4.8 (1,102)</p><span class="cc-badge">단독판매</span></div><button class="cc-heart" type="button">♡</button></article>
