                <article class="cc-card cc-result-card"><a class="cc-result-card__poster" href="/concerts/25"><img src="/images/sample/poster-cas.svg" alt="Cigarettes After Sex 포스터"></a><div class="cc-result-card__body"><span class="cc-concert-card__category">콘서트</span><h3 class="cc-result-card__title"><a href="/concerts/25">Cigarettes After Sex Live in Seoul</a></h3><p class="cc-result-card__line">2026.05.30(토)</p><p class="cc-result-card__line">잠실실내체육관</p><p class="cc-result-card__line">서울</p><p class="cc-rating"><span class="cc-rating__star">★</span> 4.8 (834)</p><span class="cc-badge">단독판매</span></div><button class="cc-heart" type="button">♡</button></article>
